Description:
    Installs ActionText with Tailwind CSS integration for this project.
    This generator replaces the default rails action_text:install.

Example:
    bin/rails generate action_text

    This will create:
        Migration: db/migrate/[timestamp]_create_action_text_tables.rb
        Partial: app/views/active_storage/blobs/_blob.html.erb
        CSS: Add Trix editor Tailwind styles
        JS: Install and configure Trix editor with TypeScript
